The Adafruit_LSM6DS library allows you to use the inertial measurement unit (IMU) available on the MTDuino board.
it has a 3-axis accelerometer and a 3-axis gyroscope. The IMU is connected through I2C on the MTDuino boardâ€™s microcontroller.

